09">daṃ</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="zh-CN">故曰此世应为我之世</span><span ttm:role="x-roman">天摩诃满 荼揭谛檀</span></p><p begin="2:55.307" end="2:58.035" itunes:key="L15" ttm:agent="v1"><span begin="2:55.307" end="2:55.870">Hi</span> <span begin="2:55.931" end="2:56.223">ma</span><span begin="2:56.296" end="2:56.584">ma</span> <span begin="2:56.631" end="2:56.900">ja</span><span begin="2:56.900" end="2:57.144">gad</span> <span begin="2:57.144" end="2:57.404">i</span><span begin="2:57.404" end="2:58.035">daṃ</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="zh-CN">此世已为我之世</span><span ttm:role="x-roman">天摩诃满 荼揭谛檀</span></p><p begin="2:58.109" end="3:00.554" itunes:key="L16" ttm:agent="v1"><span begin="2:58.109" end="2:58.445">Pūr</span><span begin="2:58.445" end="2:58.787">ṇen</span><span begin="2:58.787" end="2:59.047">du</span><span begin="2:59.047" end="2:59.320">r</span> <span begin="2:59.320" end="2:59.544">i</span><span begin="2:59.544" end="2:59.784">va</span> <span begin="2:59.784" end="2:59.984">śo</span><span begin="2:59.984" end="3:00.212">bha</span><span begin="3:00.212" end="3:00.554">te</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="zh-CN">诸法清净如月明</span><span ttm:role="x-roman">普难渡罗 缚娑婆多</span></p><p begin="3:00.962" end="3:03.634" itunes:key="L17" ttm:agent="v1"><span begin="3:00.962" end="3:01.637">Pūr</span><span begin="3:01.731" end="3:02.070">ṇen</span><span begin="3:02.070" end="3:02.381">du</span><span begin="3:02.437" end="3:02.684">vat</span> <span begin="3:02.684" end="3:02.919">a</span><span begin="3:02.919" end="3:03.166">khaṇ</span><span begin="3:03.166" end="3:03.634">ḍam</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="zh-CN">诸法圆融如月满</span><span ttm:role="x-roman">普难渡缚 阿揭拏檀</span></p><p begin="3:06.813" end="3:25.581" itunes:key="L18" ttm:agent="v1"><span begin="3:06.813" end="3:09.314">Saṃ</span><span begin="3:09.701" end="3:12.023">bha</span><span begin="3:12.527" end="3:14.998">vo</span> <span begin="3:15.447" end="3:17.562">vi</span><sp